:{{A|VO Side1 hk1 balaway 101.ogg}} '''Balaway:''' I'm already retired from appraising ancient relics. So unless this detector is some kind of precious treasure...
:{{A|VO Side1 hk1 hook 195.ogg}} '''Hook:''' Look at this! The detector's probe broke off, can you fix it?
:{{A|VO Side1 hk1 balaway 102.ogg}} '''Balaway:''' ...
:{{A|VO Side1 hk1 balaway 103.ogg}} '''Balaway:''' Oh ho ho, this certainly is a rare relic! Let me take a closer look...
:{{A|VO Side1 hk1 hook 196.ogg}} '''Hook:''' Yes, look extra close! You have to help Hook fix it!
:{{A|VO Side1 hk1 balaway 104.ogg}} '''Balaway:''' This device... I've been in the business for a long time, but never have I seen an ancient relic like this one before.
:{{A|VO Side1 hk1 balaway 105.ogg}} '''Balaway:''' I think this is probably beyond repair. But still, it is a rare treasure. Even broken, I'd be willing to pay a high price for it. What do you say?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Can we trust your appraisal?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_201214209-->
::{{A|VO Side1 hk1 balaway 106.ogg}} '''Balaway:''' The detector's probe is gone, it's like searching for something without eyes or ears. Now it's nothing more than a pile of junk with no practical value.
::{{A|VO Side1 hk1 balaway 107.ogg}} '''Balaway:''' I'm willing to offer a generous price for this thing. So, do you want to sell it or not?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Can you tell me more about it? I intend to sell it.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_201214210-->
::{{A|VO Side1 hk1 balaway 108.ogg}} '''Balaway:''' The detector's probe is gone, it's like searching for something without eyes or ears. Who's going to want a pile of junk?
::{{A|VO Side1 hk1 balaway 109.ogg}} '''Balaway:''' I don't believe any other stores will buy it off you. Come on, I'll give you a nice deal.
