::'''Balaway:''' Shh &mdash; quiet! Who told you that?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Why did you start doing appraisals again?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_812100004-->
:::'''Balaway:''' I'm just meeting the demands of the market. Someone needs to appraise all those treasures being dug up out from the {{Color|keyword|nobold=1|ancient ruins}}. Why not me?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Why so mysterious about everything though?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_812100006-->
:::'''Balaway:''' Because I, Balaway, have a reputation to protect here. Getting back into this line of business isn't anything you want publicly known, otherwise I'll be up to my neck in it &mdash; again.
:::'''Balaway:''' I won't mince words with you: If you bring me something that isn't from the {{Color|keyword|nobold=1|ancient ruins}}, I won't be interested.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_801210101_17-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_801210101_17-->
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What's up with the ancient ruins?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_812100009-->
::'''Balaway:''' Haven't you heard? When the mineral deposits were being prospected, a huge underground ruin was also dug up.
::'''Balaway:''' It's likely Old World architecture and has plenty of relics buried in it. Loads of relic hunters went there.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Why haven't you gone down yourself?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_812100012-->
:::'''Balaway:''' That's not for me. I can just have other people bring me relics for a nice appraisal fee. Isn't that much safer than doing it myself?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Are there really ancient relics to be found there?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_812100014-->
:::'''Balaway:''' Of course. In the past week alone I've seen more treasure than the entire past year!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_812100015-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_812100015-->
::'''Balaway:''' I'm ethically bound to advise you: Some people who go into those ruins never come back out, and some who bring me relics to appraise are covered head-to-toe in wounds.
::'''Balaway:''' If you're still keen, head to the {{Color|keyword|nobold=1|Great Mine}} and take a look. And if you find anything worth keeping, bring it over to me. Everything's negotiable!
